===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

#A unit of measure (length or distance) equal to 5,280 [[feet]] (8 [[furlong]]s) in the U.S.Customary/[[imperial|Imperial]] system of measurements. One mile is equal to 1.609344 km.<sup>[http://www.onlineconversion.com/length_common.htm ref]</sup>
